How to annotation OTU table using atlas-utils and USEARCH

#input data

ZOTU.fasta  ZOTU_table.txt

#annotation using UBC(USEARCH RDP Naive Bayesian Classifier algorithm implementation)

usearch -nbc_tax  zotus.fa  -db  rdp_16s_v16_sp.fasta -strand both -tabbedout classify.txt -log  classify.log -threads 24

#reorder OTU table

fastx-utils view  zotus.fa | tsv-utils  reorder  otutab_raw3.txt  - >ZOTU-tab.txt

#annotation ZOTU table

cut -f1,4  classify.txt | atlas-utils  annotation -  zotu-tab.txt  >zotu-tab.annotation.txt

#summary:

Now, you have  1. reordered ZOTU-tab.txt, 2.zotu-tab.annotation.txt
